Klavan: &quot;It&rsquo;s not about the goal but it feels great to have three points today. It was a crazy game in the end. That we took them three points in the end is massive.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klavan: &quot;We have such a great team and today we showed it again. We kept on going. It&rsquo;s never easy here. When you remember that the last game was only two days ago as well, everybody was ready and stepped up.&quot;

Klavan: &quot;Of course not, if you see what length and weight they have in their team it&rsquo;s not easy but it&rsquo;s always important to play our game. That was important today.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klavan on his goal: &quot;Before we had the free kick I knew I wanted to run there. This is a great chance when somebody from the second post hits it back. I just wanted to secure the goal. Maybe it would have gone in but there were a lot of Burnley players around.&quot;

